                            <p class="blocktext">
                                Recreational pursuits offered by the Water Sports Centre range from kayaking and bravo sailing to snorkeling for adults.
                            </p>
                            <p class="blocktext">
                                GrandBlue can also organize a fishing excursion and diving with Sailing Club Divers, Bangladesh’s longest running Five Star Dive Centres.
